room_title: Escape room "Cyber Case" by Escape Room Clearwater Beach in Tampa
room_description: You have a briefcase that has been left by the group Anonymous, and as history has shown that it is not one to be taken lightly. Your team has been commissioned by the United States Government to thwart an imminent Cyber attack while you gather clues, solve puzzles, combine intel, decipher secret messages and trigger hidden mechanisms to stop an imminent Cyber Attack.
